(16, 1, '2018-07-19 11:57:59', '2018-07-19 10:57:59', '<h2 class=\"h4\"><span style=\"color: #283371; font-weight: normal;\">Following its acquisition by Perrigo in August 2014, Warman-Freed has become the UKâ€™s first â€˜learning pharmacyâ€™, seeking to provide insights and intelligence into the day-to-day running of a typical pharmacy operation.</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">The Learning Pharmacy allows us to gather and share real world learning. It presents a unique opportunity to learn about pharmacy from within; we can learn from real patients, behaviours and situations and then share this learning back with our pharmacy colleagues across the UK and Ireland.</p>\r\nAdding a fully-functioning retail pharmacy to our business, is part of our commitment to Pharmacy and empowering pharmacists to be strong pillars of the community. We look to provide them with the support and products to grow their business and make greater efficiencies for the NHS. Our aim is to help Pharmacy thrive, leveraging the collective expertise at Perrigo and in partnership with pharmacies across the UK.\r\n\r\nWarman-Freed is located in Golders Green, North London and is open 8.30am â€“ Midnight every day of the year.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-472 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/perrigo/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Warman_Freed_433.jpg\" alt=\"Warman_Freed\" width=\"1280\" height=\"888\" />', 'The Learning Pharmacy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-learning-pharmacy', '', '', '2018-08-31 10:20:25', '2018-08-31 09:20:25', '', 8, 'http://localhost/perrigo/?page_id=16', 0, 'page', '', 0),
