(18, 1, '2018-07-19 11:58:07', '2018-07-19 10:58:07', '<h2 class=\"h4\"><span style=\"color: #283371; font-weight: normal;\">At Perrigo, we are committed to conducting business with integrity, fostering a safe work environment, caring for our communities and minimising our impact on the environment. </span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Perrigo views Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) not only as measuring the impact of our global operations, but also as recognising our efforts to ensure that how we achieve results is just as impactful as the results themselves. We have a long history of environmentally sound and efficient operations, safe and healthy working conditions and active participation in the communities where we work.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">We believe in conducting business through our Core Values of Integrity, Respect and Responsibility. We believe our commitments to sustainability and our ability to recognise the impact we have on our environment has contributed greatly to our ability to thrive in today\'s business landscape.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Perrigo Foundation</h3>\r\nThe Perrigo Company Charitable Foundation is a private, non-profit organisation wholly funded by Perrigo Company plc. The Foundation\'s mission is to provide financial support to non-profit organisations that enhance the health, well-being and education of individuals and families in communities that Perrigo serves.\r\n\r\nAs part of Perrigoâ€™s social responsibility plan, every country receives a budget every year to make a difference to our communities.\r\n\r\nIn the UK, there are four different ways we support our communities\r\n<ol class=\"features-list\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4>Site charity of the year</h4>\r\nOur employees across each of our sites vote to support a local cause that means a lot to them.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4>Supporting a UK-wide initiative</h4>\r\nOur employees across the UK vote to support one charity and organise a programme of events and activities to support them.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4>Matching charity activities</h4>\r\nWe know that we have a lot of employees who are very passionate about a charity close to their hearts and want to help support this, which is why we offer a charity matching scheme.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4>Volunteer programme</h4>\r\nIf our people volunteer their time outside of work to a charitable organisation, we donate money towards that charity.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'Corporate Social Responsibility', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'csr', '', '', '2018-08-30 11:49:07', '2018-08-30 10:49:07', '', 8, 'http://localhost/perrigo/?page_id=18', 0, 'page', '', 0),
