(239, 1, '2018-08-16 12:57:22', '2018-08-16 11:57:22', '<h2 class=\"p copy-l\"><span style=\"color: #00a5db;\">We are the UK and Ireland\'s No1 player in the niche specialty oral liquid prescription formulations market with manufacturing operations across two MHRA and FDA approved sites in Leeds. </span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">We manufacture and supply over 150 specialist liquid medicines for leading international branded pharma companies as well as formulations under our own brand â€“ Rosemont. All have a minimum 9-month shelf life with proven stability data available on request.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">The portfolio comprises of licensed and unlicensed (\'specials\') designed to offer a better treatment experience to paediatric and older patient groups who may find tablets too difficult to swallow or where the tablet formulation is the inappropriate strength.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">We have a continual programme of new product development and support education through an innovative range of resources for healthcare professionals and patients. Including a 24-hour helpline for healthcare professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #283371;\">Serving Patient Needs</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Dysphagia or swallowing difficulty preventing patients taking their medication can be associated with many reasons, for example:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Stroke</li>\r\n 	<li>Parkinson\'s disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Alzheimer\'s or dementia</li>\r\n 	<li>Old age, loss of muscle tone, less saliva being produced</li>\r\n 	<li>Head and neck cancer</li>\r\n 	<li>Cerebral palsy</li>\r\n 	<li>Learning disability</li>\r\n 	<li>Children unwilling or unable to swallow tablets designed for adults</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #283371;\">Extensive Product Range</span></h3>\r\nOur products can be used across a wide range of therapeutic areas including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Anaethesia</li>\r\n 	<li>Cardiovascular</li>\r\n 	<li>Central Nervous System</li>\r\n 	<li>Endocrine</li>\r\n 	<li>Gastro-Intestinal System</li>\r\n 	<li>Infection</li>\r\n 	<li>Malignant Disease &amp; Immunosuppression</li>\r\n 	<li>Musculoskeletal System</li>\r\n 	<li>Nutrition and Blood</li>\r\n 	<li>Obstetrics, Gynaecology and Urinary-Tract Disorders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #283371;\">The Rosemont Commitment</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Extensive Product range</strong>Â â€“ liquid medicines for many therapeutic areas including cardiovascular, endocrine, central nervous system, gastro-intestinal and musculo-skeletal.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Exceptional Product quality</strong>Â â€“ we produce all our medicines to the same exacting GMP standards, so whether they are licensed products or \'Specials\' the quality will be the same through batch manufacturing.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Reliable delivery</strong>Â â€“ delivery within 48 hours in over 99% of orders and within 24 hours available on request.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Outstanding Customer Service</strong>Â â€“ dedicated and knowledgeable customer service team who provide expert support for our customers</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Proven Shelf life</strong>Â â€“ for both licensed and \'Specials\'. Generally our \"Specials\" have a minimum 9 month shelf life.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Award-winning Educational Resources</strong>Â â€“ we are a key partner in the education of healthcare professionals in the field of medicines management in patients with dysphagia or swallowing difficulties. We have a wide range of resources designed to help healthcare professionals deliver the best possible care. Also, extensively researched patient information leaflets.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Healthcare professional advice service</strong>Â â€“ 24 hour professional advice line available 365 days a year.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Rosemont Pharmaceuticals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '37-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-16 12:57:22', '2018-08-16 11:57:22', '', 37, 'http://localhost/perrigo/37-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
