(360, 1, '2018-08-29 11:42:08', '2018-08-29 10:42:08', '<h2 class=\"h4\"><span style=\"color: #283371; font-weight: normal;\">The team at Perrigo has a wealth of experience in quoting for, winning and implementing significant Contract Manufacturing opportunities.</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Having collaborated with major blue chip brands for over 4 decades, in traditional â€œtollâ€ manufacturing, contract new product development and supply from in-house Intellectual Property, Perrigoâ€™s support structure is geared to delivering projects on time and in full. Brands can be assured of a confidential and professional service, with an experienced team and a facility focused on delivering quality affordable healthcare products.</p>', 'Multi-format Pharmaceutical  Contract Manufacturing & Packing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-29 11:42:08', '2018-08-29 10:42:08', '', 27, 'http://localhost/perrigo/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(361, 1, '2018-08-29 11:44:49', '2018-08-29 10:44:49', '<h2 class=\"h2\"><span style=\"color: #283371; font-weight: normal;\">Perrigo is one of the fastest growing healthcare companies in the world, and an in-dustry leader in pharmaceutical technologies. We develop, manufacture and dis-tribute over-the-counter (OTC) branded and non-branded consumer goods, as well as prescription (Rx) pharmaceuticals.</span></h2>\r\nYou may have heard of some of our iconic household brands including Nytol, Solpadeine, Tiger Balm, NiQuitin, Jungle Formula, Dermalex, XLS-Medical and family favourite TCP. We also produce over 160 liquid medicines helping to treat a variety of conditions, such as musculoskeletal and joint diseases, cardiovascular disease, infections, swallowing problems and more.\r\n\r\nAt Perrigo, we are unapologetically passionate about making a difference to health - relentlessly making quality healthcare products accessible and affordable for people around the world.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-29 11:44:49', '2018-08-29 10:44:49', '', 8, 'http://localhost/perrigo/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
